Blurb::
Select between cumulative or complementary-cumulative functions
Description::
The selection of a 
 -* CDF - cumulative distribution function
 -* CBF - cumulative belief function
 -* CPF - cumulative plausibility function
vs. a
 -* CCDF - complementary cumulative distribution function
 -* CCBF - complementary cumulative belief function
 -* CCPF - complementary cumulative plausibility function
can be performed with the \c distribution keyword
and the choice of \c cumulative or \c complementary.

This selection also
defines the sign of the reliability or generalized reliability
indices.
